Arduino Electronic Skeeball Machine - Design Notes
=======================================================

8 Foot Runway
	•a good size for household use
___________________________________________________

Marquee features
	•game over indicator
	•winner indicator
	•free game indicator
	•digital score display
	•digital ball count display
	•attract mode
____________________________________________________

Game Over Light
	•is on if ball count = 9
	•1 LED
____________________________________________________
 
Winner Light
	•is on if current score is >= 250 points
	•triggers unique melody 
  	•2 LEDs
_____________________________________________________
  
Free Game Light
	•is on if current score is equal to 450 points
	•triggers unique melody
	•1 LED
______________________________________________________

Digital Score Display
	•displays the current score to user

  	20 LEDs total
  	----------------------------
  	hundreds place 		7 LEDs
  	tens place 		7 LEDs
  	ones place 		6 LEDs
____________________________________________________
  
Digital Ball Count Display
	•displays the current ball count to user

  	7 LEDs total
	------------------------------
	ones place		7 LEDs
____________________________________________________
  
Score Pockets (10,20,30,40,50)
	•increments score display
	•score column contains 5 cherry switches
_____________________________________________________
  
Gutter Pocket (0)
	•increments ball count display
	•triggers pocket sound
	•contains 1 cherry switch
_____________________________________________________
  
Coin Mechanism
	•adds credit
  	•accepts US quarters, rejects all other currency
_____________________________________________________
  
Start Button
	•adds credit
______________________________________________________

Speaker
	•plays idle music
	•plays pocket sounds
	•plays simple melodies
_______________________________________________________
  
Servo Motor
	•controls ball release mechanism
________________________________________________________
  
Liquid Crystal Display
	•displays user inputs / settings
	•contrast controled by potentiometer
________________________________________________________

User Input Interface
	•contains 4 push buttons
	•manipulates setting
________________________________________________________

Arduino Ethernet Shield
	•adds internet connectivity
________________________________________________________

8 Position Dip Switch
	•enables/disables idle music
	•enables/disables start button
	•enables/disables free games
	•defines 1 credit as equal to 1,2,3, or 4 quarter(s)
	•controls other user preferences
	•allows future expansion
________________________________________________________
  
Android Companion App
	•http client / database application
________________________________________________________

High Score feature
	•high score read from / written to database
	•high score triggers unique melody
========================================================